    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for a dependable daily driver without the high price tag of a newer model. The engine and transmission are in good working order, though the car does show its age with some cosmetic blemishes, including minor scratches on the exterior and some wear on the interior upholstery. Mechanically, it runs well, but it could benefit from a standard tune-up and perhaps some suspension work in the near future to restore a smoother ride. Overall, it's a solid, functional car that is ready for the road but would appreciate a little bit of cosmetic and mechanical attention from its next owner.",
