      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, which serves as a testament to diligent ownership and consistent servicing. This specimen offers a refined driving experience, characterized by its robust mechanical performance and a well-preserved aesthetic profile. Every aspect of this vehicle has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for safety and operational excellence. It represents a sophisticated choice for the discerning driver who prioritizes both performance and long-term value. We invite you to experience the superior composure of this automobile through a private viewing.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner. I\u2019m more than happy to answer any questions or have you come by for a test drive whenever you\u2019re free. Looking for a smooth, friendly sale!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This engine features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering linear power and immediate throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power distribution. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, addressing common platform weak points. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension arrangement. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical components\u2014including the cross-drilled rotors and ventilated calipers\u2014are in excellent operating order for spirited driving.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean title. No major issues. Ready for immediate pickup.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of a well-cared-for driver's car. Mechanically, it is in top form; the engine is responsive, the transmission shifts crisply, and it has passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection within the last month. The interior remains remarkably clean, with no tears in the upholstery and all electronic features\u2014including the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system\u2014functioning perfectly. On the exterior, the paint holds a deep, brilliant shine, though a detailed walk-around will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from standard use. It sits on a set of tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining and comes with a complete set of service records. This is a reliable, turn-key car that offers a premium driving experience without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 31800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated design. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and aesthetic presentation. Featuring a clean title and a consistent service history, it offers an exceptional balance of luxury and dependability. Secure this high-value acquisition today and experience uncompromised performance.",
      "price": 36500.0,
