      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014it runs like a dream and still looks great pulling into the driveway! It\u2019s clearly been well-loved and is just waiting for its next adventure. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
