    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound A80 chassis powered by the iconic 2JZ-GTE inline-six. This unit retains its factory sequential twin-turbocharger configuration, delivering linear power through the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. The drivetrain is anchored by a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring balanced torque distribution. Recent technical updates include a fresh timing belt, water pump, and valve cover gaskets to address common age-related seepage. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the structural integrity and powertrain compression remain within nominal factory specifications. An excellent candidate for the purist looking for a high-performance foundation without the 'mint' premium.",
